This is a Java weather app.

incorporating java .awt
bufferReader
API to openweather using current weather , forecast and icon image URL endpoints.

enter your      city, country(format) and see your weather.

install the required .jar files and compile and run. 
you can replace the dynamic images with your own.
Watch your file names. 

This app with retrieve weather from specified locations.
It will show you the forcast for that area.
Details and a weather icon will be shown.
There is a dynamic background that will change depending on time of day the app is used.
you can search your previos searches.
you can toggle between C* amd F* tempurature units.

